ney-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/hole_melissa_courtney-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/hole_melissa_courtney-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/hole_melissa_courtney-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hole">Hole</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/courtney-love">Courtney Love</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/melissa-auf-der-maur">Melissa Auf Der Maur</a>本周再次回到工作室，这是二十多年来的首次 - 请查看下面的照片。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="286" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/courtney-love-hole-solo-music-liverpool-interview-2819456"><b>Courtney Love：“我感觉自己是摇滚史上最幸运的混蛋”</b></a></li></ul><p> Auf Der Maur 于 1994 年贝斯手 Kristen Pfaff 去世后加入乐队，并在乐队呆了五年，录制了 1998 年的专辑“Celebrity Skin”。</p><p>现在，两位音乐家 24 年来首次在录音室重聚，一系列照片已在 Instagram 上分享。目前尚不清楚他们是否一起录制过任何东西。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8LJGU1oL8k/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div st